ORDER_TAKEN_OR_CANCELLED: Swap: Order is already taken or cancelled
NONCE_TOO_LOW: Swap: Order nonce is below the required minimum
SIGNATURE_INVALID: Swap: Signature does not match the specified order
SENDER_BALANCE_LOW: Swap: Sender token balance is insufficient
SIGNER_BALANCE_LOW: Swap: Signer token balance is insufficient
SENDER_ALLOWANCE_LOW: Swap: Sender has not approved its token for trading
SIGNER_ALLOWANCE_LOW: Swap: Signer has not approved its token for trading
SENDER_UNAUTHORIZED: Swap: Sender of the transaction must be authorized by the sender on the order
SIGNER_UNAUTHORIZED: Swap: Signatory of the signature must be authorized by the signer on the order
SENDER_TOKEN_KIND_MISMATCH: Swap: Sender token contract does not match the specified kind
SIGNER_TOKEN_KIND_MISMATCH: Swap: Signer token contract does not match the specified kind
SENDER_TOKEN_KIND_UNKNOWN: Swap: Sender token kind is not recognized
SIGNER_TOKEN_KIND_UNKNOWN: Swap: Signer token kind is not recognized
SELF_TRANSFER_INVALID: Swap: Signer and sender wallets must be different
VALIDATOR_INVALID: Swap: Signature is intended for a different swap contract
SENDER_INVALID_ID: Swap: Sender must not include 'id' for the specified token kind
SENDER_INVALID_AMOUNT: Swap: Sender must not include 'amount' for the specified token kind
SIGNER_INVALID_ID: Swap: Signer must not include 'id' for the specified token kind
SIGNER_INVALID_AMOUNT: Swap: Signer must not include 'amount' for the specified token kind
SENDER_ETHER_LOW: Wrapper: Sender ether balance is insufficient
SIGNER_ETHER_LOW: Wrapper: Signer ether balance is insufficient
SENDER_WRAPPER_ALLOWANCE_LOW: Wrapper: Sender has not approved the wrapper
SIGNER_WRAPPER_ALLOWANCE_LOW: Wrapper: Signer has not approved the wrapper
MSG_SENDER_MUST_BE_ORDER_SENDER: Wrapper: Sender of the transaction must be the sender on the order
SENDER_KIND_MUST_BE_ERC20: Delegate: Sender token kind must be ERC20
SIGNER_KIND_MUST_BE_ERC20: Delegate: Signer token kind must be ERC20
TOKEN_PAIR_INACTIVE: Delegate: Not trading the specified token pair
ORDER_AMOUNT_EXCEEDS_MAX: Delegate: Amount exceeds the amount available
DELEGATE_UNABLE_TO_PRICE: Delegate: Not quoting the requested amount or token pair
PRICE_INVALID: Delegate: Order price must match the quoted price
SENDER_WALLET_INVALID: Delegate: Order sender wallet must match the trade wallet
